data.description: 1805 Jerez Loop has officially come to the market and is ready to be showcased. This beautiful and modern custom build home features a large master bedroom, with walk-in closet and contemporary restroom finishes. Furthermore, this home possesses two other spacious rooms that keynote their large closet space and up to date clean finishes. Lastly letting us focus on this homes avant garde kitchen, living and dining room that are sure to catch your eye.
